---
title: Rosemary Butter Pork & Dauphinoise Potatoes with Baby Rainbow Carrots & Baby Broccoli
description: Bring some French flair to your table with this sublime dish! Starting with a premium pork fillet and some creamy dauphinoise
potatoes, and finishing with sweet roasted baby rainbow carrots and crisp sautéed baby broccoli, you're in for a treat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easter-rosemary-garlic-lamb-264e1270.jpg
